metadata.name: The Waiting Room
metadata.description:
"The Waiting Room" represents life itself, full of things that make sense and have no sense at all, things chaotic and organized. It is a place of choice, movement and stillness. It is a place of birth and  a slow walk towards the end. Look closely and you might just see yourself in one of those fellows that figuring it all out.

The digital art comes with a physical piece.
